  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Valyrian</b> can refer to:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Valyria\" title=\"Valyria\">Valyria</a>, a ruined city in Essos</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_peninsula\" title=\"Valyrian peninsula\">Valyrian peninsula</a>, a ruined peninsula in Essos</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_Freehold\" title=\"Valyrian Freehold\">Valyrian Freehold</a>, a former realm ruled from Valyria</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Valyrians\" title=\"Valyrians\">Valyrians</a>, the ethnic group that inhabited the Valyrian peninsula and founded the Valyrian Freehold</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/High_Valyrian\" title=\"High Valyrian\">High Valyrian</a>, the language of Valyria</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/High_Valyrian#Bastard_Valyrian\" title=\"High Valyrian\">Bastard Valyrian</a>, the language spoken in the Free Cities and in the cities from Slaver's Bay, though all have different dialects, derived from High Valyrian</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_(ship)\" title=\"Valyrian (ship)\">Valyrian</a></i>, a galley owned by <a href=\"/index.php/Salladhor_Saan\" title=\"Salladhor Saan\">Salladhor Saan</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Valyrian&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_roads\" title=\"Valyrian roads\">Valyrian roads</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_sphinx\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Valyrian sphinx\">Valyrian sphinx</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_steel\" title=\"Valyrian steel\">Valyrian steel</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_steel_dagger\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Valyrian steel dagger\">Valyrian steel dagg